name: I Read The Rules So You Don’t Have To
description: We love you, rule-readers! 📜 Dig into those fun rules exceptions in this TeeTurtle original "I Read The Rules So You Don’t Have To" navy blue t-shirt!

name: Chaotic Neutral
description: "What's wrong with being the wild card?" 🤷‍♂️ Bring the fun in this TeeTurtle original "Chaotic Neutral" black t-shirt!

name: Game Knight
description: "There's no time to joust—I have card games to play!" 🃏Get your game night priorities straight in this TeeTurtle original "Game Knight" charcoal gray t-shirt!

name: Ready For Adventure
description: "Bring on the adventure!" 🛡 Embark on a quest in this TeeTurtle original "Ready For Adventure" black t-shirt!

name: Natural 20
description: Now that's what we call a "natural" 20! 🌸 Celebrate your best rolls in this TeeTurtle original "Natural 20" apple green t-shirt!

name: Dexterity 10, Wisdom 0
description: "This may not be an effective training method, but it sure is fun!" 🏹 Try something new in this TeeTurtle original "Dexterity 10, Wisdom 0" denim blue t-shirt!

name: I Might Need These Later (Dice)
description: "I've rounded up every single dice I could get my paws on, so one of these has to lead me to victory!" Be UBER prepared for your next battle in this charcoal TeeTurtle original "I Might Need These Later (Dice)" t-shirt!

name: D20 Landscape
description: It's your turn! 🎲 Roll the dice and enter a fantasy world in this navy TeeTurtle original "D20 Landscape" t-shirt!

name: Born to Explore
description: "I may look small, but my game character is big and strong!" Pick up this navy TeeTurtle original "Born to Explore" t-shirt for all your adventures to come!

name: Back in My Day
description: These youngins don't know how easy they have the game-life nowawdays. If you claimed to be a video game technician solely based on your ability to fix consoles by blowing on them, then you'll love this gray, TeeTurtle original "Back in My Day" t-shirt, featuring an adorable panda.

name: Cosplay Turtles
description: "Could anyone direct us to the Shell Convention?" 😆 Show off your love of cons and costumes in this TeeTurtle original "Cosplay Turtles" charcoal gray t-shirt!

name: Pew Pew Panda
description: Tees are social creatures, so make sure to get them lots of friends!

name: Gamer Mom
description: "No need to wait for nap time! I can dominate no matter how many little cubs are around." 🎮  Kick virtual butt like the awesome mom you are in this navy TeeTurtle original "Gamer Mom" t-shirt!

name: I'm a 20 in Charisma
description: "Hey! Social intelligence is a type of intelligence." 📣 Own your strengths and shortcomings in this TeeTurtle original "I'm a 20 in Charisma" navy blue t-shirt!

name: D20 Dragon
description: If you want this D20, you have to get past the dragon first! 🐲 Hope for a good roll in this TeeTurtle original "D20 Dragon" black t-shirt!

name: I'm a Lover and a Fighter
description: "What? I can do both!" ⚔️💕 Show you contain multitudes in this TeeTurtle original "I'm a Lover and a Fighter" black t-shirt!

name: Strength Check
description: "Hey! Gamers can work out too!" 💪 Pump some iron in this TeeTurtle original "Strength Check" silver t-shirt!

name: Speed 10, Dexterity 0
description: "My hands are shaking and I can hear my heartbeat but I am definitely not falling asleep anytime soon!"☕️ Overcaffeinate in this TeeTurtle original "Speed 10, Dexterity 0" silver t-shirt!

name: Bedtime Lag
description: Don't you dare shame us for staying up gaming! 🎮 Explain your lifestyle to nosy friends in this TeeTurtle original "Bedtime Lag" navy t-shirt! Tees are social creatures, so make sure to get them lots of friends!

name: Blood Moon Dragon
description: "With the blood moon comes transformation." Transform in this TeeTurtle original "Blood Moon Dragon" black t-shirt!

name: Autumn Fox
description: It's time for Fall 🍂 Grab a sweater, enjoy some apple cider, go pumpkin picking, and appreciate the beautiful leaves! Pick up the red TeeTurtle original "Autumn Fox" t-shirt and jump in your own leaf pile!

name: I'm Doing Side Quests
description: "Trust me I bet these will reaaaaaally pay off!" Big, small, or impromptu, choose your own adventures in this navy TeeTurtle original "I'm Doing Side Quests" t-shirt!

name: Hex-olotl
description: "Don't cross me or you'll get hurt-alotl!" 🪄 Hex your nemesis (only if they deserve it!) in this TeeTurtle original "Hex-olotl" black t-shirt!

name: Player 1 Panda
description: Are you Player 1 or Player 2? 🎮  Team up in this TeeTurtle original "Player 1 Panda" black t-shirt, and get our "Player 2 Red Panda" t-shirt to match with your partner!
